Trung: Photon mapping, depth of field, part of BVH, kd-tree
Akshay: Transmissive material, anisotropic material, progressive rendering,
Rachel:  Volumetric rendering, part of kd-tree, part of BVH, denoiser, pixel compression, Perlin noise generator

To run photon mapping, make sure you uncomment #define PHOTON_MAP in mygl.h
In your scene, also add this tag to enable photon map integrator:

	<integrator type="photonMap">
		<maxDepth>5</maxDepth>
		<indirectPhotons>15000</indirectPhotons>
		<causticPhotons>20000</causticPhotons>
		<neighborSamples>100</neighborSamples>
		<maxDistance>100</maxDistance>
	</integrator>

The "photon_map.xml" file provides a sample scene.
